ReinforcementBendRules.r1:
Minimum mandrel diameter dop for reinforcement is taken depending on the diameter of the rod ds, not less than:
- for plain rods
dop = 2.5ds at ds < 20 mm;
dop=4ds at ds ≥ 20 mm;
- for deformed rods
dop=5ds at ds < 20 mm;
dоп=8ds at ds ≥ 20 mm;

ReinforcementBendRules.r2:
Minimum mandrel diameter to avoid damage to reinforcement is taken:
4Ø rod diameter Ø ≤ 16 mm;
7Ø at rod diameter Ø > 16 mm;
